This paper deals with image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model utilizes LSTM, which is a popular deep learning technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of textual features and their integration with image representations, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.CL, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.IR.
